        },
        {
            "title": "〈熱門股〉友達挾兩大題材 周漲17%站回所有均線",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">面板大廠友達 (2409-TW) 挾 Micro LED 技術切入 AI 光通訊應用，加上 Touch Taiwan 登場在即、股價先行暖身，連假前無懼大盤走弱，延續漲停攻勢、收漲逾 5%，單周漲幅 17%，站回所有均線。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">友達技術長廖唯倫表示，Micro LED 具備精密巨量轉移以及光學設計的特性，可應用在 CPO 跟矽光子領域，成為下一代 AI 短距高速傳輸的關鍵技術，公司現階段也在跟 AI 供應鏈合作、送樣產品。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-33e3da85-acbc-392f-a998-8a3a97484f04-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">廖唯倫進一步指出，目前市場普遍認為，未來 2-3 年 CPO 跟矽光子技術將達商業化規模，屆時對友達及相關供應鏈來說也將迎來「光進銅退」的商機。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">友達也將於 4 月 8 日登場的 Touch Taiwan 2026 智慧顯示展覽會，以「映現世界 透見未來 Reveal the World. Reveal the Future.」為主題，率領集團公司與合作夥伴，展示 Micro LED 量產成熟度與跨域落地應用。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"友達日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/z8dvWbwQ9tmuTiU.ya3U_Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/cnyes_hk_559/b3893af4c0ed7205b3f86957388c70d0\" width=\"580\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:580px\">友達日 K 線圖</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap read-more-vendor break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>更多鉅亨報導</span><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"群創Touch Taiwan聚焦互動顯示 展示多元場域應用\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:群創Touch Taiwan聚焦互動顯示 展示多元場域應用;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6404611?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">群創Touch Taiwan聚焦互動顯示 展示多元場域應用</a><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"富采整合友達CPO模組 應用Micro LED搶攻AI資料中心互連商機\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:富采整合友達CPO模組 應用Micro LED搶攻AI資料中心互連商機;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6404278?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">富采整合友達CPO模組 應用Micro LED搶攻AI資料中心互連商機</a></p></div>",
