        {
            "title": "情報報告警告:伊朗對荷莫茲海峽的封鎖將持續",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FSohemaPO_oD8FNraAnbyA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_6_M_1440048362.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 美國最新情報評估顯示,伊朗短期內不太可能放棄對荷莫茲海峽的控制,該國將其對這條全球最關鍵石油通道的掌控視為對抗華盛頓的主要籌碼。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士透露,德黑蘭打算繼續扼制這條水道以維持全球能源價格高企,對唐納德·川普總統施加直接經濟壓力,以確保在這場持續五週的衝突中獲得有利的退出條件。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>\"大規模破壞武器\"及市場影響</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國主導的軍事行動最初目標是瓦解伊朗的區域影響力,但分析師警告,這場戰爭可能無意中達成了相反的效果。德黑蘭成功阻斷了承載全球20%石油貿易的通道,展示了一種\"大規模破壞武器\",部分專家認為這比核威懾更具威力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-04d659c8-a10e-347c-9b77-d2df6ec71608-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗的封鎖已將原油價格推升至多年高位,正值共和黨為11月關鍵期中選舉做準備之際,在美國引發通脹擔憂。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">實際戰術情況使任何重新開放這條21英里寬通道的軍事解決方案變得複雜。即使美軍奪取沿海領土,伊斯蘭革命衛隊(IRGC)仍保有利用低成本無人機和從伊朗內陸深處發射的導彈攻擊來干擾商業交通的能力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國際危機組織的阿里·瓦埃茲指出:\"只需一兩架無人機就足以嚇阻船隻\",突顯了這種不對稱風險使得該水道目前對大多數商業運輸公司而言無法投保。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>戰後收入與威懾策略</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">情報報告進一步指出,伊朗的長期策略涉及將臨時封鎖轉變為永久監管框架。前中央情報局局長比爾·伯恩斯表示,德黑蘭將收取\"通行費\"的能力視為資助戰後重建的重要機制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預計伊朗將利用其\"發現的\"海上影響力,超越即時財務收益,在與美國的任何最終和平交收中要求長期安全保證和威懾措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管白宮堅稱總統\"有信心\"海峽將很快開放,但政府也暗示北約盟國和海灣國家對這些能源走廊的依賴度更高,應在海上安全任務中發揮更積極的作用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種立場轉變凸顯了當前談判的困難,因為美國試圖重新開放貿易路線,同時避免陷入曠日持久且代價高昂的地面戰爭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%B0%8D%E8%8D%B7%E8%8E%AB%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E5%B0%87%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-233107530.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-04 07:38:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美法官維持撤銷鮑威爾相關傳票裁決 檢方誓言提起上訴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vd3T.V1_ZZGFTFBfXbZu8Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f1150ebf2edbda1bac130c26c2560ee1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國司法部要求繼續調查<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"聯儲會\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>大樓翻修成本問題的請求被法院駁回，此舉為後續上訴鋪平道路，該案最終可能提交至最高法院。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國哥倫比亞特區聯邦地區法院首席法官James Boasberg維持了撤銷美國檢察官Jeanine Pirro向聯儲會發出的兩份大陪審團傳票的判決。這些傳票與針對聯儲會大樓翻修工程支出以及聯儲會主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾在國會作證內容的刑事調查有關。Pirro的辦公室曾要求<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Boasberg\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Boasberg;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Boasberg\">Boasberg</a>重新考慮其撤銷傳票的決定。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-38e22930-acde-3de9-83ee-227f8e1c6d82-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Boasberg在4月3日的裁定中表示：「政府的論點遠不足以說服法院作出不同裁決。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Aaron Schwartz/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.U5XSFc3_qpq80taAJZuxQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b2fd1d41f45cf7f7f721010f1a427984\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Aaron Schwartz/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項裁決是聯儲會獨立性與司法部調查權之間法律爭議的最新進展。這場爭議還可能拖延總統唐納德·川普提名的聯儲會主席人選凱文·沃什的確認程序。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會不予置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Pirro的發言人表示：「我們絕對會對司法機關干預我們使用大陪審團的行為提起上訴。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Boasberg在3月裁定撤銷相關傳票，稱司法部未能提供足夠證據。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Judge Denies Pirro Motion to Revive Quashed Fed Subpoenas (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E6%92%A4%E9%8A%B7%E9%AE%91%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E5%82%B3%E7%A5%A8%E8%A3%81%E6%B1%BA-%E6%AA%A2%E6%96%B9%E8%AA%93%E8%A8%80%E6%8F%90%E8%B5%B7%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-203450806.html",
